{"tid":1676962,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[正視聽]集中金店排龍係好有用架！","createTime":"2019-10-26T18:33:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T19:02:39.000Z","uid":280192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"50db5a92a63af0e6615da2f85435ab7bf738d34b","tid":1676962,"uid":280192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T18:33:48.000Z","msg":"集中排好處：<br />\n<br />\n1.排隊，本身就係示威。黑衣人排兩個鐘龍門，就等於示威兩個鐘。警察唔通拉你排隊食飯？係最安全嘅示威方法。如果門口三千食客超長龍，等位唔食，示威效果拍得住遊行架。<br />\n<br />\n2. 同路人喜歡夠深黃、有得打卡、好食底食嘅鋪，呢d完全係人性。如果違反人性，活動好易散。正常發展落去，多人排的大店總係有多d優點，會逐漸跑出，然後開分店，打出版圖。<br />\n<br />\n3. 試想有一日龍門隊短短，排15分鐘食到。仲有邊個知道黃懲罰個活動存在緊？無圖無真相，過一排呢個活動就會無左。<br />\n<br />\n我明白分散排隊好處，d錢容易救到小商店。所以我完全唔反對人買小店。<span style=\"color: red;\">但請勿視集中排龍的人，係齋排無貢獻。純粹正視聽。</span><br />\n<br />\n希望買黃店呢條戰線，一樣係兄弟爬山。有人幫手長龍造勢，有人分散獎勵，各有各做。"},{"pid":"dcc51312ecea31cb6170ca5f4b998ef50f1b9bf9","tid":1676962,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T18:34:15.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f422917543543e0070b3797d7979e35771e04b","tid":1676962,"uid":274538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T18:35:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oibyUGf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoibyUGf.jpg&h=b4dd4bae&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZHddUGh.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZHddUGh.gif&h=03474c51&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5cbbc34e69686f67bfb139b11698d67c98807e84","tid":1676962,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T19:02:39.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]